name: Paradox Metaverse
description: The Paradox Eco-System is designed to be a world where people can live, work, be entertained and interact with others! An opportunity to earn sustainable yield in the Paradox Metaverse. whilst playing a action/adventure free-roam game built on the Unreal Engine 5, to Paradox Events which will be hosting Youtubers Boxing in 2023. Using the Parapad Launchpad to launch similar projects into the cryptospace.
